
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Simulador RVV &mdash; Lideran&ccedil;a Equipacare 2026</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
:root{
  --navy:#2D4A68;--navy-dark:#1E3350;--steel:#4A7A9B;
  --teal:#3BB8C0;--teal-lt:#E6F7F8;
  --lime:#B8CC10;--lime-lt:#F4F7D6;
  --bg:#F2F5F8;--white:#FFF;
  --text:#1E2D3D;--muted:#5A7080;--border:#D8E1EA;
  --red:#D94F3D;--red-lt:#FCECEA;
  --orange:#E8863A;--orange-lt:#FEF0E6;
  --green:#3BAA5E;--green-dk:#2A8048;--green-lt:#E6F4ED;
  --shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(45,74,104,.12);
  --r:10px;--rs:6px;
}
body{font-family:'Segoe UI',system-ui,Arial,sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-size:13px;line-height:1.45;}

/* HEADER */
.hdr{background:var(--navy);padding:10px 22px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;box-shadow:0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.3);}
.hdr img{height:38px;background:#fff;border-radius:4px;padding:3px;}
.hdr-info{flex:1;}
.hdr h1{color:#fff;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;}
.hdr p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);font-size:11px;margin-top:1px;}
.hdr-badge{background:var(--lime);color:var(--navy-dark);font-size:10px;font-weight:800;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:.8px;text-transform:uppercase;}
.hdr-btns{display:flex;gap:8px;}
.btn-hdr{padding:7px 14px;border:none;border-radius:var(--rs);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;transition:opacity .15s;}
.btn-hdr:hover{opacity:.85;}
.btn-exp{background:var(--lime);color:var(--navy-dark);}
.btn-imp{background:rgba(255,255,255,.18);color:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);}

/* TABS */
.nav{background:var(--navy-dark);display:flex;padding:0 22px;gap:2px;overflow-x:auto;}
.nav button{background:none;border:none;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;padding:13px 18px;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:3px solid transparent;transition:all .18s;white-space:nowrap;}
.nav button:hover{color:#fff;}
.nav button.act{color:#fff;border-bottom-color:var(--lime);}

/* LAYOUT */
.pane{display:none;padding:16px 22px;max-width:1320px;margin:0 auto;}
.pane.act{display:block;}
.g2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px;}
.g3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:14px;}
.g4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:14px;}

/* CARDS */
.card{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r);box-shadow:var(--shadow);margin-bottom:14px;overflow:hidden;}
.ch{padding:9px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;color:#fff;}
.ch.navy{background:var(--navy);}
.ch.steel{background:var(--steel);}
.ch.teal{background:var(--teal);}
.ch.lime{background:var(--lime);color:var(--navy-dark);}
.cb{padding:14px 16px;}

/* INPUTS */
.ig{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:9px;}
.ig label{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;min-width:220px;flex-shrink:0;}
.ig input[type=number]{width:88px;padding:5px 8px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--rs);font-size:13px;color:var(--text);}
.ig input[type=number]:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--teal);}
.ig .unit{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;}
.ig select{padding:5px 8px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--rs);font-size:13px;color:var(--text);}
.sec-lbl{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;color:var(--muted);margin:14px 0 8px;}

/* TABLES */
.tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;}
.tbl th{background:var(--bg);color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;padding:9px 11px;text-align:left;border-bottom:2px solid var(--border);}
.tbl td{padding:7px 11px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);vertical-align:middle;}
.tbl tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}
.tbl tbody tr:hover>td{background:#F7FAFB;}
.tbl input[type=number]{width:70px;padding:4px 6px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;font-size:12px;text-align:right;}
.tbl input[type=number]:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--teal);}
.tbl-wrap{overflow-y:auto;max-height:420px;border-radius:0 0 var(--r) var(--r);}
.tbl-wrap .tbl thead th{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:2;background:#E8EDF2;box-shadow:0 1px 0 var(--border);}

/* PILLS */
.pill{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:12px;}
.p-green{background:var(--green-lt);color:var(--green-dk);}
.p-orange{background:var(--orange-lt);color:var(--orange);}
.p-red{background:var(--red-lt);color:var(--red);}
.p-grey{background:var(--bg);color:var(--muted);}
.p-navy{background:#E8EDF4;color:var(--navy);}

/* POOL METRICS */
.mbox-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;}
.mbox{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r);box-shadow:var(--shadow);padding:11px 14px;border-left:4px solid var(--teal);}
.mbox.navy{border-left-color:var(--navy);}
.mbox.lime{border-left-color:var(--lime);}
.mbox.red{border-left-color:var(--red);}
.mbox.steel{border-left-color:var(--steel);}
.mbox .mv{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);}
.mbox .ml{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-top:2px;}
.bar{height:6px;border-radius:4px;margin-top:5px;transition:width .3s;}

/* INFO / WARN BOXES */
.ibox{background:var(--teal-lt);border-left:4px solid var(--teal);border-radius:0 var(--rs) var(--rs) 0;padding:10px 14px;margin:10px 0;font-size:13px;color:var(--navy);}
.wbox{background:#FEF9E7;border-left:4px solid #F0C040;border-radius:0 var(--rs) var(--rs) 0;padding:10px 14px;margin:10px 0;font-size:13px;color:#5A4A00;}
.rbox{background:var(--red-lt);border-left:4px solid var(--red);border-radius:0 var(--rs) var(--rs) 0;padding:10px 14px;margin:10px 0;font-size:13px;color:var(--red);}
.fbox{background:var(--lime-lt);border-left:4px solid var(--lime);border-radius:0 var(--rs) var(--rs) 0;padding:10px 14px;margin:10px 0;font-size:13px;color:var(--navy-dark);}

/* FLOW STEPS */
.flow{display:flex;margin:10px 0;}
.fst{flex:1;background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:10px;position:relative;}
.fst:first-child{border-radius:var(--r) 0 0 var(--r);}
.fst:last-child{border-radius:0 var(--r) var(--r) 0;}
.fst+.fst::before{content:'›';position:absolute;left:-12px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);font-size:20px;color:var(--teal);background:#fff;padding:0 2px;}
.fst .num{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--teal);color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:7px;}
.fst h4{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:5px;}
.fst p{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5;}

/* SCALE VISUAL */
.scale-vis{display:flex;border-radius:var(--rs);overflow:hidden;margin:12px 0;}
.sv{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;text-align:center;padding:10px 5px;line-height:1.4;}
.sv.a{background:var(--red-lt);color:var(--red);}
.sv.b{background:var(--orange-lt);color:var(--orange);}
.sv.c{background:var(--green-lt);color:var(--green);}
.sv.d{background:#D9F0E3;color:var(--green-dk);}
.sv .sv-sub{font-size:10px;font-weight:400;opacity:.8;margin-top:3px;}

/* KPI GROUP CARDS */
.kpig-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:11px;}
.kpig{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r);box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow:hidden;}
.kpig-hdr{padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.kpig-hdr.navy{background:var(--navy);}
.kpig-hdr.steel{background:var(--steel);}
.kpig-hdr.teal{background:var(--teal);}
.kpig-mult{font-size:18px;font-weight:800;}
.kpig-body{padding:12px;}
.kpi-row{margin-bottom:10px;}
.kpi-lbl{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.kpi-peso{color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;}
.gate-tag{font-size:10px;background:var(--red-lt);color:var(--red);border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;font-weight:700;}
.kpi-inp-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.kpi-inp-row input[type=number]{width:80px;padding:5px 8px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;text-align:right;}
.kpi-inp-row input[type=number]:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--teal);}
.ab{font-size:10px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;}
.ab-z{background:var(--red-lt);color:var(--red);}
.ab-l{background:var(--orange-lt);color:var(--orange);}
.ab-o{background:var(--green-lt);color:var(--green);}
.ab-m{background:#D9F0E3;color:var(--green-dk);}
.kpig-result{margin-top:9px;padding-top:8px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.kpig-result .krl{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);}
.kpig-result .krv{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;}
.gate-warn{background:var(--red-lt);border-radius:var(--rs);padding:5px 9px;font-size:11px;color:var(--red);font-weight:600;margin-top:6px;display:none;}

/* ELEGÍVEIS / RESULTADO TABLE */
.exp-btn{width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid var(--steel);color:var(--steel);font-size:14px;font-weight:700;background:none;cursor:pointer;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .15s;}
.exp-btn.open{background:var(--navy);border-color:var(--navy);color:#fff;}
.row-exp{cursor:pointer;}
.row-exp:hover>td{background:#EEF4F9 !important;}
.det-row{display:none;}
.det-row.open{display:table-row;}
.det-cell{padding:0 !important;border-bottom:2px solid var(--teal) !important;}
.det-inner{padding:13px 13px 13px 42px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:11px;}

/* BLOCK CARDS (DETAIL) */
.blk{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--rs);padding:11px;position:relative;}
.blk.zeroed{border-color:var(--red);background:#FEF8F8;}
.blk-title{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:7px;}
.blk-w{position:absolute;top:9px;right:9px;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);}
.blk-kpi{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:4px;font-size:12px;}
.blk-res{margin-top:7px;padding-top:7px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
.blk-coins{font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);font-size:15px;}
.blk-mult-tag{font-size:11px;background:var(--bg);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px;color:var(--steel);}
.blk-total{grid-column:1/-1;background:var(--teal-lt);border-radius:var(--rs);padding:11px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}

/* CARTEIRA CARDS */
.cart-card{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r);box-shadow:var(--shadow);margin-bottom:14px;overflow:hidden;}
.cart-hdr{padding:11px 16px;background:var(--steel);color:#fff;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;}
.cart-body{padding:14px;}
.cart-summary{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin:8px 0 12px;}
.cart-summary strong{color:var(--navy);}
.btn-add{padding:6px 14px;background:var(--teal);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:var(--rs);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;margin-top:8px;}
.btn-add:hover{background:#2FA8B0;}
.btn-del{background:none;border:none;color:var(--red);cursor:pointer;font-size:15px;padding:2px 5px;}

/* MISC */
hr.div{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:13px 0;}
.c-green{color:var(--green-dk);}
.c-orange{color:var(--orange);}
.c-red{color:var(--red);}
.c-navy{color:var(--navy);}
.fw7{font-weight:700;}
.mono{font-family:monospace;}

@media(max-width:900px){
  .pane{padding:12px;}
  .g2,.g3,.g4{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .flow{flex-direction:column;}
  .fst+.fst::before{display:none;}
  .fst:first-child,.fst:last-child{border-radius:0;}
  .fst{border-radius:0;}
  .hdr-btns{flex-wrap:wrap;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="hdr">
  <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Equipacare">
  <div class="hdr-info">
    <h1>Simulador de Remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o Vari&aacute;vel</h1>
    <p>Programa de B&ocirc;nus da Lideran&ccedil;a &middot; Apura&ccedil;&atilde;o Anual 2026</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hdr-badge">Simula&ccedil;&atilde;o</div>
  <div class="hdr-btns">
    <button class="btn-hdr btn-imp" onclick="importExcel()">&#8593; Importar Excel</button>
    <button class="btn-hdr btn-exp" onclick="exportExcel()">&#8595; Exportar Excel</button>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- TABS -->
<nav class="nav">
  <button class="act" onclick="showTab('metodologia',this)">Metodologia</button>
  <button onclick="showTab('parametros',this)">Par&acirc;metros</button>
  <button onclick="showTab('atingimento',this)">Atingimento</button>
  <button onclick="showTab('resultado',this)">Eleg&iacute;veis &amp; Resultado</button>
</nav>

<!-- ═══ TAB 1 · METODOLOGIA ═══ -->
<div id="tab-metodologia" class="pane act">

  <div class="card">
    <div class="ch navy">Como funciona o Programa de B&ocirc;nus &mdash; Vis&atilde;o Executiva</div>
    <div class="cb">
      <div class="flow">
        <div class="fst">
          <div class="num">1</div>
          <h4>Gatilho: LL M&iacute;nimo</h4>
          <p>O <strong>Lucro L&iacute;quido 2026</strong> precisa superar o valor m&iacute;nimo esperado pelos acionistas. Abaixo desse patamar, nenhum b&ocirc;nus &eacute; gerado.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fst">
          <div class="num">2</div>
          <h4>Pool: Delta &times; % Distribui&ccedil;&atilde;o</h4>
          <p>Superado o gatilho, um <strong>% configur&aacute;vel do delta</strong> (LL Realizado &minus; LL M&iacute;nimo) &eacute; destinado ao pool de b&ocirc;nus. <em>Valores inseridos em R$&nbsp;Milh&otilde;es.</em></p>
        </div>
        <div class="fst">
          <div class="num">3</div>
          <h4>Moedas: Saldo-alvo ajustado por KPIs</h4>
          <p>Cada eleg&iacute;vel parte de um <strong>saldo-alvo de moedas</strong>. O atingimento dos KPIs, bloco a bloco, ajusta este saldo para cima ou para baixo.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fst">
          <div class="num">4</div>
          <h4>Pagamento: (moedas pessoa / total moedas) &times; pool</h4>
          <p>O pool &eacute; sempre distribu&iacute;do integralmente. Se algu&eacute;m n&atilde;o performa e perde moedas, quem performou melhor recebe proporcionalmente mais &mdash; sem sobra no caixa.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ibox"><strong>Pool:</strong> (LL Realizado &minus; LL M&iacute;nimo) &times; % Distribui&ccedil;&atilde;o &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Pagamento:</strong> (Moedas Pessoa &divide; Moedas Total) &times; Pool &nbsp;<span style="opacity:.7;font-size:12px;">(LL em R$&nbsp;Mi)</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="ch steel">Escala de Atingimento</div>
    <div class="cb">
      <div class="scale-vis">
        <div class="sv a">&#10060; Abaixo m&iacute;n<div class="sv-sub">(&lt; 80%)<br>&times;0,0</div></div>
        <div class="sv b">&#9888; M&iacute;n &rarr; Alvo<div class="sv-sub">(80%&rarr;100%)<br>&times;0,8&rarr;&times;1,0</div></div>
        <div class="sv c">&#10003; Alvo &rarr; M&aacute;x<div class="sv-sub">(100%&rarr;120%)<br>&times;1,0&rarr;&times;1,2</div></div>
        <div class="sv d">&#128640; Acima m&aacute;x<div class="sv-sub">(&gt; 120%)<br>cap &times;1,2</div></div>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">Valores ilustrativos com par&acirc;metros padr&atilde;o. Os limiares e multiplicadores s&atilde;o configur&aacute;veis na aba Par&acirc;metros.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="ch teal">Estrutura de Blocos e Gatilhos</div>
    <div class="cb">
      <div class="g3">
        <div class="blk">
          <div class="blk-title">Bloco Corporativo</div>
          <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">KPIs de empresa (Faturamento + EBITDA). Aplicado a todos os eleg&iacute;veis com peso vari&aacute;vel por n&iacute;vel (20% a 100%).</p>
          <div class="ibox" style="margin-top:8px;font-size:12px;"><strong>Gatilho EBITDA:</strong> se EBITDA abaixo do resultado m&iacute;nimo, bloco corporativo = 0 para todos.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="blk">
          <div class="blk-title">Bloco de &Aacute;rea</div>
          <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">KPIs da unidade de neg&oacute;cio (Adm., Comercial, GQM, ATE, ECP, EIH). Cada escopo &eacute; calculado de forma independente. Quem tem dois escopos, tem o peso dividido por &aacute;rea.</p>
          <div class="ibox" style="margin-top:8px;font-size:12px;"><strong>Gatilho por escopo:</strong> zera apenas aquela por&ccedil;&atilde;o.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="blk">
          <div class="blk-title">Bloco de Carteira (GQM e ATE)</div>
          <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">Para Gerentes Regionais com carteira de contratos GQM e ATE. Cada contrato avaliado individualmente por Satisfa&ccedil;&atilde;o (gate), Resultado e Conformidade.</p>
          <div class="ibox" style="margin-top:8px;font-size:12px;"><strong>Gate de satisfa&ccedil;&atilde;o:</strong> contrato reprovado gera 0 moedas para aquele contrato.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wbox">
        <strong>Importante:</strong> O gatilho zera apenas aquele bloco, n&atilde;o o pagamento completo.<br><em>Ex: Se margem ECP for abaixo do m&iacute;nimo, Ger. Geral ECP perde 80% das suas moedas (peso do bloco &aacute;rea), mas mant&eacute;m os 20% do bloco corporativo.</em>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="ch navy">L&oacute;gica de Apura&ccedil;&atilde;o da Carteira (GQM e ATE)</div>
    <div class="cb">
      <div class="flow">
        <div class="fst">
          <div class="num">1</div>
          <h4>Fator de Contratos</h4>
          <p>A gest&atilde;o define as <strong>Moedas Ajustadas</strong> por pessoa (padr&atilde;o: moedas-alvo &times; peso carteira), considerando churn de contratos.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fst">
          <div class="num">2</div>
          <h4>Contratos Ativos Finais</h4>
          <p>Lista de contratos GQM e ATE vinculados &agrave;quele gerente. As moedas ajustadas s&atilde;o divididas igualmente entre os contratos.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fst">
          <div class="num">3</div>
          <h4>Gate de Satisfa&ccedil;&atilde;o</h4>
          <p>Se a nota de Satisfa&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato estiver abaixo do resultado m&iacute;nimo &rarr; moedas daquele contrato = 0 (sem compensa&ccedil;&atilde;o).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fst">
          <div class="num">4</div>
          <h4>Resultado e Conformidade</h4>
          <p>Moedas = base &times; (50% &times; mult_Resultado + 50% &times; mult_Conformidade). Pesos configur&aacute;veis.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fbox">
        <strong>F&oacute;rmula por contrato:</strong> Moedas = (Moedas Ajustadas &divide; N) &times; (50% &times; mult_Resultado + 50% &times; mult_Conformidade). Se satisfa&ccedil;&atilde;o reprovada: Moedas = 0
      </div>
      <div class="ibox" style="margin-top:10px;font-size:12px;">
